01:05:50.000 --> 01:05:53.000
How did you get into the race?

01:05:53.000 --> 01:05:58.000
I volunteered to run. I volunteered to run.

01:05:58.000 --> 01:06:04.000
I wasn't an educator.

01:06:04.000 --> 01:06:07.000
