01:06:07.000 --> 01:06:15.000
And after I could be superintendent, they changed that law.

01:06:15.000 --> 01:06:19.000
I ran against them by the spite.

01:06:19.000 --> 01:06:27.000
And by this time the voting rights act had been passed and there were a lot of blacks on the voting roles in Holmes County.

01:06:27.000 --> 01:06:32.000
But still, there are lots of counties where blacks are in a majority.

01:06:32.000 --> 01:06:38.000
