Kruger is the first time.

01:12:07.000 --> 01:12:09.000
Kruger and Durant. Kruger.

01:12:09.000 --> 01:12:17.000
That's a John and the LaFlau kind of line and a North Western part of Homes County.

01:12:17.000 --> 01:12:21.000
Well, I knew the votes I was going to get in Kruger.

01:12:21.000 --> 01:12:22.000
I knew those of them.

01:12:22.000 --> 01:12:25.000
And I was counting those votes.

01:12:25.000 --> 01:12:29.000
And that wasn't enough to put me over.

01:12:29.000 --> 01:12:35.000
But Lord and behold, when Durant came in, I won Durant.

01:12:35.000 --> 01:12:38.000
