01:16:40.000 --> 01:16:47.000
You were determined that you were going to be a good legislator. How did that work out with all of this?

01:16:47.000 --> 01:16:59.000
Well, first of all, I couldn't get the floor to house. If I stand for recognition, somebody to make a motion.

01:16:59.000 --> 01:17:09.000
I'm already standing. These poses, you know, Robert Roos of order, but he'd recognize somebody else to cut me out. And I couldn't get the floor.

01:17:09.000 --> 01:17:18.000
So one night, this is my first time. I walked out and Bill Monter, you know, Bill Monter, yes.

01:17:18.000 --> 01:17:27.000
Very, very outrageous course. Yes. And Bertilemmon, they came out. I had cleaned my desk. I had everything.

01:17:27.000 --> 01:17:37.000
